					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Another tip: if you're tracking the last $4003+x value for each channel in a variable, set it to $FF whenever the volume is 0 so that the note restarts properly. My own music engine wouldn't play consecutive notes on the triangle channel until I fixed this.</div>

